Subject: [PATCH AUTOSEL 5.4 133/134] kernel: sysctl: make drop_caches write-only
Date:   Wed, 11 Dec 2019 10:11:49 -0500
Message-Id: <20191211151150.19073-133-sashal@kernel.org>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.20.1
